(56, 'Career Counseling', 'career-counseling2', 'Career Counselling', 'Others', 'Normal', 1, 'It is the key step or main turning point of your career path and your future if you are looking for study abroad after you high school education (+2).', '<br />\r\nThis is not the major step for the students who are looking for bachelors study or higher degree. But it is the key step or main turning point of your career path and your future if you are looking for study abroad after you high school education (+2). Our expertise will explain different field studies and its major impact in socio-economic changes and upcoming major advancements in technologies and socio-economics. Knowledge of advancement in socio-economic and technologies will help you to find the best possible future job markets when you come out from you study to the world job market. This is particularly focused to students after +2 since most of the students are puzzling to find the best career path and career destination. We are aware of ineffective career selection by the student after high school education.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548227112_1.jpg', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Career Counselling', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:19:07', '2019-01-31 12:10:03'),
(57, 'Set study destination country', 'set-study-destination-country', 'Set study destination country', 'Others', 'Normal', 2, 'We will guide you for the selection of study destination according to your choice of career path too.', '<br />\r\nThis is the first step once you have considered the abroad study in your mind. We will guide you for the selection of study destination according to your choice of career path too. Because, there are different impact and value of courses of different subjects in different countries. For example; study of studying biomedical engineering in USA has highest value, studying computer application in Australia has better value.', 48, '1548227147_2.jpg', '2', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Set study destination country', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:20:47', '2019-01-31 12:10:37'),
(58, 'University or college selection', 'university-or-college-selection', 'University or college selection', 'Others', 'Normal', 3, 'Depending up on your academic performance and your study interest area, we recommend different universities and colleges within the country you selected as study destination.', '<br />\r\nAnother major step is university or colleges selection for students after higher school education; this is kind of dilemma for the students. Depending up on your academic performance and your study interest area, we recommend different universities and colleges within the country you selected as study destination. Depending up on the university or college you selected our respective education counselor will help you note down standardized test such as IELTS/TOEFL/PET/SAT etc.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548237143_1.jpg', '3', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'University or college selection', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:21:29', '2019-01-31 12:11:43'),
(59, 'Documentation', 'documentation', 'Documentation', 'Others', 'Normal', 4, 'Our documentation officer will assist you to get the documents such as SOP, LOR, Resume etc. through workshops', '<br />\r\nThis could be the hectic job for student to get documents other than academic; so, our documentation officer will assist you to get the documents such as SOP, LOR, Resume etc. through workshops; we will give the information how to get financial documents and property evaluations. Depending up on the country of study and university or colleges, you could have to submit different documents; accordingly, our documentation officer will assist you what are the documents to be prepared and to be submitted.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548227237_4.jpg', '4', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Documentation', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:22:17', '2019-01-31 12:12:47'),
(60, 'Application Submission', 'application-submission', 'Application Submission', 'Others', 'Normal', 5, 'Once you are ready in documentation, we will assist you to submit your application form to the universities or colleges of your choice.', '<br />\r\nOnce you are ready in documentation, we will assist you to submit your application form to the universities or colleges of your choice. Most of the student need help because of unfamiliar words and some immigration related words to be filed up in the university admission application forms. Accepted students will get admission letter as soon as possible through EasyLink.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548227306_5.jpg', '5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Application Submission', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:23:26', '2019-01-31 12:15:24'),
(61, 'Tuition Fee', 'tuition-fee', 'Tuition Fee', 'Others', 'Normal', 6, 'We will do our best to help the student pay the tuition fee and make our best effort for the reduction of tuition fee from the colleges and universities we are working with.', '<br />\r\nGenerally, students are asked to pay one year tuition fee by different universities or colleges. We will do our best to help the student pay the tuition fee and make our best effort for the reduction of tuition fee from the colleges and universities we are working with.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548237616_4.jpg', '6', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tuition Fee', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:24:01', '2019-01-31 12:16:39'),
(62, 'Medical Examination', 'medical-examination', 'Medical Examination', 'Others', 'Normal', 7, 'Medical examination is not mandatory for all the abroad destinations; however you may have medical examination at the port of entry or immigration.', '<br />\r\nMedical examination is not mandatory for all the abroad destinations; however you may have medical examination at the port of entry or immigration. But, some countries such as Australia, New Zealand may need so medical examination certificates. Students are not to be perplexed about the medical examination. It is simply a medical test to make sure you have not communicable disease at the time of entry at immigration.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548227366_7.jpg', '7', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Medical Examination', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:24:26', '2019-01-31 12:19:13'),
(63, 'Visa Application', 'visa-application', 'Visa Application', 'Others', 'Normal', 8, 'Our visa assistant officer will assist the student to fill up and submit the visa application form.', '<br />\r\nOur visa assistant officer will assist the student to fill up and submit the visa application form. We also assist the students to make ready for potential visa interview with different workshop and leadership trainings. Visa application is another moment where students get puzzled because of some immigration related terminologies; so, our visa and documentation offers assist students making visa application job as easy as possible. Depending up on the country you are applying for study visa or permission, it could have different terminology for study permit document either student visa or entry permit, so our visa assistant officer will assist our student either to apply entry permit or study permit.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548328409_1548227471_9.jpg', '8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Visa Application', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:24:53', '2019-01-31 12:27:26'),
(64, 'Visa Grant', 'visa-grant', 'Visa Grant', 'Others', 'Normal', 9, 'Depending up on the countries and immigration, different country has different travel documents or entry permission documents.', '<br />\r\nThis is the turning point which decide the student if you are granted for foreign study. Depending up on the countries and immigration, different country has different travel documents or entry permission documents. In Canada, students are required to get eTA sometime and visitor’s visa sometimes. For Nepalese student, visitor’s visa is needed.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548227471_9.jpg', '9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Visa Grant', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:26:11', '2019-01-31 12:23:27'),
(65, 'Pre – Departure', 'pre-departure', 'Pre – Departure', 'Others', 'Normal', 10, 'Once the student get study permit or student visa from the corresponding country of choice, students should prepare for departure and arrival in the corresponding country.', '<br />\r\nOnce the student get study permit or student visa from the corresponding country of choice, students should prepare for departure and arrival in the corresponding country. We will have different session for the students to give information on living life, cultural values in abroad.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548237321_2.jpg', '10', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pre – Departure', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:26:40', '2019-01-31 12:34:00'),
(66, 'Travel and Accommodation', 'travel-and-accommodation', 'Travel and Accommodation', 'Others', 'Normal', 11, 'Our service partners will help the students to get travel tickets and necessary foreign exchanges, travel insurance etc.', '<br />\r\nOur service partners will help the students to get travel tickets and necessary foreign exchanges, travel insurance etc. We also assist student for accomodation at the destination countries where we have our branch offices. Generally, we advise student to get accomodation provided by the university or college they are starting their study becuase college or university housing service will have best study environment and time saving for students.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 48, '1548237375_10.jpg', '11', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Travel and Accommodation', NULL, '1', '2019-01-23 01:27:13', '2019-01-31 16:52:34'),
(67, 'Message From CEO', 'message-from-ceo', 'Message From CEO', 'Main', 'Normal', 2, NULL, 'No sooner had information technology been introduced than every perspective of global advancement came to common ground following common standards. Education is the one to come into common ground and degree from the renowned university located in any corner of the world is recognized anywhere in the world. Additionally, globalization introduced the multinational companies with common economic ground and so the multicultural workplace which ultimately necessitated global workforces. Hence, international education in multicultural environment is attractive everywhere around the world.<br />\r\nAnd Yes, I am glad to introduce my team of experts in counseling, documentation and visa assistant to facilitate your dream of international education. &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Message From CEO', NULL, '0', '2019-01-23 03:46:56', '2019-01-30 16:28:17'),
(68, 'Free SOP workshop “Making Your SOP Attentive”', 'free-sop-workshop-making-your-sop-attentive', 'Free SOP workshop “Making Your SOP Attentive”', 'Main', 'Normal', 1, '15th, March 2019', '<br />\r\nSince statement of purpose (SOP) is the key document – carrying 30% - 40% admission decision weight – for admission decision by the Department or school the students are applying, SOP must be attentive and cogent to the admission application. We found majority of students are puzzling on how to write convincing SOP to the admission committee. So, we are organizing SOP workshop “Making Your SOP Attentive” on following date and venue.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvent Date: 15th March 2019<br />\r\nVenue: EasyLink Career Consultant<br />\r\nDowntown Market Dillibazar Road-29, Putalisadak Kathmandu.<br />\r\nPhone: 01-4010626 / 01-5900678<br />\r\nWeb: www.easylink.edu.np/email:info@easylink.edu.np<br />\r\nEasyLink Career Consultant is organizing SOP Workshop<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease contact us to attend for the workshop', 5, '1548833210_SOP.jpg', NULL, '1549261350_event-details-img.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Free SOP workshop “Making Your SOP Attentive”', NULL, '1', '2019-01-24 15:17:15', '2019-02-13 13:45:50'),
(69, 'Free Resume & CV workshop “Shaping Your CV or Resume”', 'free-resume-cv-workshop-shaping-your-cv-or-resume', 'Free Resume & CV workshop “Shaping Your CV or Resume”', 'Main', 'Normal', 2, '1st April 2019', '<br />\r\nAdmission officers are not that much free as we think because of overwhelming number of applications. So, one of the application documents for your admission decision should be attentive to the admission officers. They do not prefer lengthy CV or Resume as your application document. So, we are organizing Free CV &amp; Resume Workshop “Shaping CV or Resume” on the following date and venue.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvent Date: 1st April 2019<br />\r\nVenue: EasyLink Career Consultant<br />\r\nDowntown Market Dillibazar Road-29, Putalisadak Kathmandu.<br />\r\nPhone: 01-4010626 / 01-5900678<br />\r\nWeb: www.easylink.edu.np/email:info@easylink.edu.np<br />\r\nEasyLink Career Consultant is organizing Resume &amp; CV Workshop<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease contact us to attend for the workshop<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote: Participant students need to register at least 2 days in advance because you need sample<br />\r\npreparation time so that you can work on the document.', 5, '1548833234_Curriculum_resume.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Free Resume & CV workshop “Shaping Your CV or Resume”', NULL, '1', '2019-01-24 15:18:42', '2019-02-28 11:37:15'),
(70, 'Sample Document', 'sample-document', 'Sample Document', 'Next', 'Group', 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Sample Document', NULL, '1', '2019-01-25 08:34:10', '2019-01-25 08:34:10'),
(71, 'SOP', 'sop', 'SOP', 'Next', 'Attachment', 1, NULL, NULL, 70, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1549946743_SOP Guidelines.pdf', NULL, 'SOP', NULL, '1', '2019-01-25 08:34:29', '2019-02-12 10:45:43'),
(72, 'LOR', 'lor', 'LOR', 'Next', 'Attachment', 2, NULL, NULL, 70, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1549946691_LoR Sample.pdf', NULL, 'LOR', NULL, '1', '2019-01-25 08:34:44', '2019-02-12 10:44:51'),
(73, 'Introduction', 'introduction', 'Introduction', 'Main', 'Normal', 1, NULL, '<br />\r\nOnce you have been come into thoughts that you want to broaden your career with international education or degree and passionate to explore world, always, this is right time to move ahead for abroad study. We are here to assist your abroad study journey and flourish you career with world recognized education.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEasyLink Career is hub to connect best Universities and Colleges around the globe. Making you motivated for globalized education and sharpening you as global workforce is our one and only one goal. To make you competent for global work places, we help you to find your career path through landing you world’s best universities. We are highly commited to shape you as front-line warrior in global market with our expertise in career counseling, educational advising in your choice of professions. We highly encourage you one step forward for world recognized education to explore your potential and world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNot only do we assist you to set your career goal and finding career path but also make you well prepared for your move to the next educational level. For perspective undergraduate students, we provide seminars and workshops for leadership skill development. On the flip side, for perspective graduate students, we provide research knowledge and different workshops to equip you with tools and techniques for graduate research works.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Mission</strong></span><br />\r\nWe expect all the students after abroad study will be expertise in their respective study of field and will be highly skilled manpower to lead the country even the world. So, we work in the run as:&nbsp;\r\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<li>To immunize the student to flourish potential in their career path.</li>\r\n	<li>To encourage student explore the world along with their study dream.</li>\r\n	<li>To take pride in promote and support to explore all the excellencies of the student</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Vision</strong></span><br />\r\nEasyLink Career Consultants would like to work in the revolution and evolution of socio-economy of Nepal and would like to contribute through working in academia which is powerful tool for the revolutionary changes. Our vision is to identify potential of individual and encourage and nurture leadership, confidence, responsibility, and traits young learners via innovative technology and methodology.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 2, NULL, NULL, '1549261611_s-bg.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Introduction', NULL, '1', '2019-01-27 16:13:07', '2019-02-04 12:26:51'),
(74, 'Resume', 'resume', 'Resume', 'Next', 'Attachment', 3, NULL, NULL, 70, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1549946567_Resume Sample.pdf', NULL, 'Resume', NULL, '1', '2019-01-28 12:32:04', '2019-02-12 10:42:47');
